<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.7.1/css/all.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/noResult.css">
    <title>Product Not Found</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="no-results-container">
        <div class="no-results-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="no-results-message">
            <h2><%= message %></h2>
        </div>
        <div class="no-results-description">
            <p>Oops! Looks like we couldn’t find what you were looking for. Don’t worry, the internet is a big place, and there are tons of awesome things waiting to be discovered!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cool-paragraph">
            <p>Maybe <span>your dream product</span> is just a search away, or perhaps it’s on another page we haven’t found yet. Either way, we’ll keep looking if you do!</p>
        </div>
        <a href="/" class="back-to-home-btn">Go Back to Home</a>
        <div class="social-media-links">
            <a href="#" class="social-link"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a>
            <a href="#" class="social-link"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
            <a href="#" class="social-link"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FontAwesome for the search icon -->
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/a076d05399.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap/5.3.0/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
